<hr style="width: 100%; height: 2px;"><br>
<h4><a name="GradUgrad_Extra_Space"></a>Grad/Ugrad
Free Storage<br>
</h4>
Computing support has set aside 1TB disk space for undergraduate
students and another 1TB for graduate students. The space is available
for all ugrads and unaffiliated grad students.&nbsp; Support will
not be
managing or backing up the space.&nbsp; Please see the following
web
page for more details:<br>
&nbsp; <br>
<div style="margin-left: 40px;"><a
 href="http://www.ics.uci.edu/%7Elab/students/extra.php">http://www.ics.uci.edu/~lab/students/extra.php</a><br>
</div>
